51030 Cost Anomaly Alerting dynamically sets the priority of the ticket based on the value of total_impact. 
P1:
     - was total_impact >= 5000,
     - we now want it to be total_impact >= 2500.

P2
     -was total_impact >= 1000 and total_impact < 5000,
     -we now want it to be total_impact >= 750 and total_impact < 2500

P3
     - was total_impact < 1000,
     - we now want it to be total_impact < 750.
